author: JCSunsfan
title: Is Jon Leuer for real
text: Quote: Originally Posted by JCSunsfan We saw it in games against us last year. He performed well when filling in for injured players with Memphis. Players in camp-PJ- in particular said he will surprise and he is quite athletic. Now he drops 17 and 14 against Cousin and in less than 20 mins of pt. Will we have to wait until regular season games to be convinced? I have been saying it on other sites that I think this team would be just fine rolling with Teletovic and Lueur in the event of a Kieff trade. This game only seems to solidify this stance.
